These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: polish, colombian, american, nigerian, spanish, dutch, argentine
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: climbing, lacrosse, tennis, rowing, ice-hockey, soccer, handball
 1. the polish is between the nigerian and the argentine##2
 2. the colombian is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 4. the spanish is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the nigerian##1
 7. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who's sport is tennis##2
 8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the argentine##1
 9. the spanish is on the left of the dutch##1
10. the spanish is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
11. the dutch is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | polish | argentine | colombian    | american | spanish   | dutch    |
| Sport         | soccer  | lacrosse   | rowing | climbing | tennis   | handball | ice-hockey |

