.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
There 7 different types of food: banana, corn, cranberry, broccoli, onion, apricot, kiwi
There are 7 different nationalities: spanish, japanese, mexican, canadian, egyptian, indonesian, malaysian
1. the indonesian is on the far left##1
2. the person eating cranberry is between the person eating apricot and the indonesian##2
3. the japanese is on the right of the spanish##1
4. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the mexican##1
5. the person eating corn is in the middle##1
6. the egyptian is on the left of the spanish##1
7. the malaysian is on the left of the person eating corn##1
8. the person eating onion is on the left of the canadian##1
9. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Food          | onion | cranberry | apricot | corn | kiwi | banana      | broccoli  |
| Nationality   | indonesian | canadian  | malaysian     | mexican     | egyptian  | spanish | japanese |

