.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: indonesian, brazilian, turkish, nigerian, colombian, argentine, italian
7 different pets are kept: hedgehog, dog, frog, guinea-pig, ferret, goldfish, mouse
 1. the colombian is on the left of the indonesian##1
 2. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 3. the owner of the ferret is the italian##1
 4. the turkish is on the left of the argentine##1
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the nigerian is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 7. the indonesian is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the mouse and the nigerian##2
 9. the indonesian is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
10. the brazilian is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | italian | colombian | indonesian | brazilian   | nigerian | turkish | argentine |
| Pet           | ferret | goldfish     | dog     | frog | guinea-pig   | hedgehog   | mouse    |

