.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, soy-milk, coffee, cola, milk, almond-milk
There are 7 different nationalities: indonesian, british, spanish, egyptian, german, japanese, canadian
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the spanish##1
 2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the german##1
 3. the japanese is on the right of the egyptian##1
 4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the german##1
 5. the indonesian is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the egyptian is between the person drinking soy-milk and the japanese##2
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle##1
 8. the egyptian is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is the british##1
10. the indonesian is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk    | cola  | coffee  | hot-chocolate  | almond-milk      | milk       | mirinda |
| Nationality   | german | egyptian | japanese | canadian | indonesian | spanish | british  |

