.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: dubstep, pop, salsa, gospel, indie, trance, ambient
The people use 7 different means of transport: jet-ski, trike, taxi, snowmobile, quad-bike, airplane, subway
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is the fan of pop##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is between the fan of ambient and the fan of dubstep##2
4. the fan of trance is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
7. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
8. the person driving the trike is the fan of gospel##1
9. the fan of indie is the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel      | indie | dubstep | salsa | ambient      | pop      | trance |
| Transport     | trike | airplane | subway       | jet-ski | taxi | quad-bike | snowmobile |

