.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  manager, librarian, freelancer, social-worker, journalist, designer, architect
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: skiing, rugby, skateboarding, basketball, ice-hockey, biathlon, sailing
1. the freelancer is on the left of the architect##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the journalist##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the librarian is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the designer is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the manager##2
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
8. the designer is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | journalist | manager | social-worker | designer | librarian | freelancer     | architect |
| Sport   | skateboarding   | basketball    | sailing    | ice-hockey      | rugby  | skiing | biathlon |

