 3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's sport is soccer##2
 5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is the person drinking sprite##1
 8. the person drinking water is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 9. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person drinking juice##2
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | sprite | soy-milk    | almond-milk | mirinda   | water | tea    | juice |
| Sport      | basketball | weightlifting | soccer    | skateboarding | water-polo    | snowboarding | badminton  |

