 5. the designer is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking tea##2
 7. the security-guard is on the right of the dancer##1
 8. the manager is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 9. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
10. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking sprite##2
11. the designer is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
