.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: superhero, drama, western, musical, zombie, crime, documentary
The people use 7 different means of transport: jet-ski, car, scooter, ship, boat, roller, van
1. the person watching superhero movies is the person driving the roller##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is between the person driving the van and the person driving the boat##2
4. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1
6. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
7. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
8. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
9. the person driving the van is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | musical     | crime | zombie | western | documentary  | superhero |
| Transport     | scooter | ship | boat   | jet-ski     | van    | car | roller   |

