.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, juice, soy-milk, sprite, almond-milk, water
The people have 7 different hobbies: puzzles, dancing, baking, skydiving, sudoku, fishing, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking sprite and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
9. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate  | lemonade       | water         | sprite         | soy-milk   | juice        | almond-milk |
| Hobby      | traveling | baking | puzzles | sudoku | dancing | fishing | skydiving  |

