 3. the person drinking 7up is the person eating lime##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 6. the person eating zucchini is the person drinking avocadoade##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is the person eating watermelon##1
 8. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person eating zucchini##2
10. the person drinking coffee is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Beverage   | 7up   | soy-milk | almond-milk | coffee   | hot-chocolate   | sprite     | avocadoade  |
